    "name": "Wanderlost",
    "steam_appid": 1403030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "通过<strong>收集</strong>、<strong>耕种</strong>、<strong>垂钓</strong>、<strong>制作</strong>、<strong>建造</strong>、<strong>陷阱</strong>、<strong>加固</strong>、<strong>探索和掠夺</strong>等方式，开启你的后启示录统治。 <br><br>进入一片荒野，除了身上的衣服之外一无所有；穿越到处都是丧尸和野生动物、充满敌意的荒野。寻找<strong>食物</strong>、<strong>水</strong>和<strong>住所</strong>对于生存至关重要，但你也可以超越单纯生存的范畴，享受可持续的生活、安全，甚至实现个人对环境的支配。<br><br>《Wanderlost》世界是由程序生成的，因此你可以选择一个方向，并开始无止境的探索。在每次新游戏中，你的体验都将是独一无二的，并且会面临意想不到的挑战。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/c66d1a15cdaacc09334049d729f714ce.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=350 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/c66d1a15cdaacc09334049d729f714ce.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/c66d1a15cdaacc09334049d729f714ce.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>主要特点</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/30beed2c2799e3f6a041ec9d65a0c836.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=518 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/30beed2c2799e3f6a041ec9d65a0c836.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/30beed2c2799e3f6a041ec9d65a0c836.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>基地建造</strong><br>随着你积累的资源越来越多，一开始的木栅栏最终会演变成一个庞大的基地。用金属墙加固你的地盘，或者设计一个迷宫来击倒丧尸，而不会导致任何结构性破坏。也许你想专注于基础设施并选择建造井、烟囱和地窖，而不是墙、炮塔和陷阱。 <br><br>如果你还有时间，何不再建造一座花园？再铺上地砖，就是最完美的基地布局了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/5b2d9e5f9107b4e08a662aa530fac705.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=522 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/5b2d9e5f9107b4e08a662aa530fac705.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/5b2d9e5f9107b4e08a662aa530fac705.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>掠夺和探索</strong><br>风险越大，回报越大。《Wanderlost》中有9种生物群，每种都有独特的危险和资源。旧美国被遗弃的基础设施丧尸密度最高，但在这些现代区域可能会找到荒野无法提供的战利品。毕竟，枪和冰箱可不是树上长出来的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/512cf4345510a6634c603777c8bd4e1a.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=516 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/512cf4345510a6634c603777c8bd4e1a.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/512cf4345510a6634c603777c8bd4e1a.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>耕种</strong><br>制作一把锄头，开始耕种吧！在你的冒险之旅中找到宝贵的种子，并制作用于打理花园的工具。开垦你周围的土地以维持生计，尽管这需要时间和精力。 <br><br>等到你的劳动成果丰收可能需要几周，但这项投资可以提供储备物资，帮助你度过冬天。只要确保你能保住辛苦劳动的成果就行！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/3adf50cf8e6fe98754d607e2a546a4dd.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=518 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/3adf50cf8e6fe98754d607e2a546a4dd.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/3adf50cf8e6fe98754d607e2a546a4dd.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>垂钓和狩猎</strong><br>为自己准备一餐饭，获得重要的资源，提升你的生存水平。用收集到的兽皮保暖，并制作鱼钩和鱼竿，去钓更大更好的鱼。垂钓可以持续低风险地提供食物，而狩猎可以获得兽皮等宝贵的制作资源，以度过寒冷的季节。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/e19368902c63bd32edbf17ebbdfb5de8.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=518 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/e19368902c63bd32edbf17ebbdfb5de8.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/e19368902c63bd32edbf17ebbdfb5de8.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>收集</strong><br>收集木材、矿石和纤维等资源，用于制作许多物品、住所、武器、工具等。大多数资源都需要工具才能获得，砍倒一棵树需要斧子，挖出一棵植物需要铲子，挖出石头需要十字镐。 <br><br>普通资源包括木材和石头，但一些高级制作配方需要更稀有的材料。在这个世界中搜寻稀有的生物群和材料，比如提供重要泥炭和沼泽钢的沼泽。多样化的世界生物群可以激励探索，还可以决定一个基地位置是好是坏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/ec75d09b823601da71803afdf6d75e70.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/ec75d09b823601da71803afdf6d75e70.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/ec75d09b823601da71803afdf6d75e70.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>战斗</strong><br>一个丧尸用棍子就可以打倒，但要对付更多丧尸，需要更先进的设备。你是隐匿狙击手还是挥舞武士刀的疯子？游戏中提供了超过75种不同的近战武器、弓和枪械，可以实现多种可能的配装和游戏风格。 <br><br>你甚至可以选择通过超快速度和陷阱能力来保护自己，战斗只是最终手段。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/478884dd99e5a5bea56c69a62238c4d2.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=518 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/478884dd99e5a5bea56c69a62238c4d2.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/478884dd99e5a5bea56c69a62238c4d2.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>制作和准备</strong><br>利用狩猎和掠夺远征之间的休息时间非常重要：制作弓箭、编织绳索用于建造建筑、剥掉兽皮用于制革、为武器重装弹药等等——准备是成功的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/5545a88d8889489c24c31d59f93d5ba2.poster.avif?t=1740697636\" width=518 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/5545a88d8889489c24c31d59f93d5ba2.webm?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1403030/extras/5545a88d8889489c24c31d59f93d5ba2.mp4?t=1740697636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>角色定制</strong><br>虽然为了生存必须与丧尸作战，但《Wanderlost》还有深层次的RPG机制，能够为玩家提供各种有趣的反馈；你每杀死一个丧尸，制作一个工具，砍下一棵树，都会离下一等级更近。升级后，即可为你的配装的下一个强大专长分配属性点。",
